# Component File Conventions

All distinct, reusable components must be extracted into their own files following this structure:

- Root folder: `components/`
- Group related components in a themed subfolder: `components/<theme>/`
- Each file is named `<name>.component.tsx`

## Examples

```
components/zone-card/zone-card.component.tsx
components/button/button.component.tsx
components/avatar/avatar.component.tsx
```

## Rules

- Never place component files directly in `components/` — always use a subfolder
- The subfolder name and file name should share the same theme/name
- Import using the full path: `import { ZoneCard } from '@/components/zone-card/zone-card.component'`
- Inline components (not reused outside their parent file) do not need to be extracted
